      "comment": "MIDWEEK SCOTCHES (1) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished third (18.27) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Winning claims. TULLOCH ROAD (4) jumped quickly and led throughout to score two back then well held latest finishing a 15 length 8th at this track (18.49). Should be about the money. SCOTCH LASS (3) box seated early before forging to the lead turning and lifting to score (17.63) at this track in a Maiden over 300m. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Should feature again. SHIPLEY'S GIRL (2) generally performs well here at this distance.",
